    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of a wide variety of museums where collections are amassed and typically presented to give a chronological perspective of the history of a city, town, region, group of people, etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
